data.description: Introducing a charming 3 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom townhome, nestled in the heart of Marietta. Interior of the home has just been freshly painted! Step inside and discover a flexible layout with a versatile floorplan design for comfortable living.  The downstairs offers a convenient bedroom, providing flexibility for guest, a home office or a cozy den. You will find two additional spacious bedrooms on the top level, ensuring privacy and ample space for everyone. The primary bedroom boasts an en suite bathroom, creating a peaceful retreat after a long day. The kitchen overlooks the welcoming family room that includes a fireplace, allowing for seamless interaction and entertaining. Have a cup of coffee in the morning or a glass of wine at night on the generous size deck off of the family room. The two car garage offers convenient parking and additional storage options. This townhome provides easy access to shopping, dining, parks, and other amenities ensuring a convenient and enjoyable lifestyle. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this charming townhome your own!
